<br/>

<p>(a) Where is the center of the hyperbola?</p>
<p style="margin-left:30px"><m> C: \hspace{3px} \big( </m> <fillin characters="3" name="ans1x"/>  <m> , </m> <fillin characters="3" name="ans1y"/>  <m> \big) </m></p>
<p/>

<br/>

<p>(b) Determine the principal axis of the hyperbola.</p>
<p style="margin-left:30px"><fillin characters="8" name="ans2"/> </p>
<p/>

<br/>

<p>(c) Find the length of the transverse axis of the hyperbola.</p>
<p style="margin-left:30px"><fillin characters="15" name="ans3"/> </p>
<p/>

<br/>

<p>(d) Find the coordinates of the vertices of the hyperbola.</p>
<p style="margin-left:30px"><m> V: \hspace{3px} \big( </m> <fillin characters="3" name="ans4x"/>  <m> , </m> <fillin characters="3" name="ans4y"/>  <m> \big) </m></p>
<p style="margin-left:30px"><m> V': \hspace{3px} \big( </m> <fillin characters="3" name="ans5x"/>  <m> , </m> <fillin characters="3" name="ans5y"/>  <m> \big) </m></p>
<p/>

<br/>

<p>(e) Determine whether each of the following points is on the hyperbola or not.</p>

<tabular style="margin-left:30px">
  <row height="30px">
    <cell width="200px">(i) <m>(</m><m>{-13}</m><m>,</m> <m>{-29}</m><m>)</m></cell>
